name: Vessels 192: Helene
description: Part of the wealthy elite Helene is a philanthropist to her core.  She is quietly repulsed by the decadence surrounding her and by the sheer waste of it all. She plays along with the status and role she has been born to but does whatever she can to help those fortunate than herself.  Seen as a heroine by many of the colony inhabitants, she has stirred up some resentments in her own class.  She doesn’t care a jot though darling.
